{"tid":454027,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"吳文遠向梁振英掟三文治失準判囚","createTime":"2017-10-31T17:57:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T02:23:06.000Z","uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3b5b21dfca3192cf5af4f05e21410f2c41e4f23d","tid":454027,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T17:57:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1745196435588405&amp;id=715486135226112\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1745196435588405%26id%3D715486135226112&d=XhJKvJGZCZrAMg57pUK6GGowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=9c92db3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1745196435588405&amp;id=715486135226112</a><br />\n<br />\n社民連主席吳文遠去年立法會選舉投票日，在票站向時任行政長官梁振英投擲三文治，但擊中梁振英後面的署理總督察。西九龍裁判法院裁定吳文遠普通襲擊罪成，判監3星期，獲准以1千元保釋等候上訴。<br />\n<br />\n署任主任裁判官蘇惠德裁決時表示，被告並非誠實可靠證人，又說被告與梁振英不是朋友，只是在示威場面見過；被告當時不發一言投擲物品，亦相信梁振英不會貿然接住物件，因此認為被告只為自己開脫。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官又說從映像及證供顯示，物品是由前方「飛出」，肯定梁振英看不到被告，最終「誤中副車」<span style=\"color: red;\">。裁判官認為被告是蓄意投擲，以表對政府不滿，</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"></span>考慮所有證供等後，裁定被告罪成。<br />\n<br />\n吳文遠求情時說基層生活受壓逼，最後途徑就是反抗，任何刑罰均不具阻嚇性。但裁判官指，無論被告的意見有多高尚，法庭不會容許任何暴力行為，因此刑罰須具阻嚇力，防止他人仿效。法庭考慮到被告不認罪，亦沒有求情因素，判處被告入獄3星期，但接納他申請保釋上訴。<br />\n<br />\n吳文遠在判刑後說，徵詢法律意見後，再決定就定罪、還是刑期上訴。<br />\n#香港電台 #港台電視31 #港台電視32 #十點半新聞天地 #吳文遠 #梁振英"},{"pid":"d0f0f71db7c7b50b6773fd5b5d7a8e3a2c4ed8b6","tid":454027,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T17:59:07.000Z","msg":"紅字咁都畀你諗到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"556bab4a0d8655d7ba4415bac30a5feaee76c3af","tid":454027,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T17:59:45.000Z","msg":"懷疑判三個禮拜咁重係因為掟唔準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab11a701fc5e32397112a410fce8a0fdf9e4514","tid":454027,"uid":5489,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T18:00:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/01/020027_70e88defab846dabacbc7ff608eb6e92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F01%2F020027_70e88defab846dabacbc7ff608eb6e92.jpg&h=07d5fd4c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/01/020029_6566f0ad71f5e26af62ab3a2308d1d65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F01%2F020029_6566f0ad71f5e26af62ab3a2308d1d65.jpg&h=03becf0b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4aebbde98d714b5a2953e2f61bf7ebec562d7c1","tid":454027,"uid":27866,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T18:02:42.000Z","msg":"低能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  掟中cy香港就獨立到？"},{"pid":"5b7dc8bf14f2522b349c5b00dcb18784ca27846b","tid":454027,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T18:05:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/01/020027_70e88defab846dabacbc7ff608eb6e92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F01%2F020027_70e88defab846dabacbc7ff608eb6e92.jpg&h=07d5fd4c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/01/020029_6566f0ad71f5e26af62ab3a2308d1d65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F01%2F020029_6566f0ad71f5e26af62ab3a2308d1d65.jpg&h=03becf0b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n有啲似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.